<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/223585.Never_Call_Retreat"><img alt="Never Call Retreat: Lee and Grant: The Final Victory (Gettysburg, #3)" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1389533002l/223585._SY160_.jpg" />
